  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators hypothesize that bevacizumab instilled into the vitreous after primary
      retinal detachment surgery will reduce the formation of proliferative vitreoretinopathy and
      subsequent retinal re-detachment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
